headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock for Long-Term Investors and 2 We Ignore
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.

headline: After stints at Nike and Kohl’s, Elevance Health’s CDIO pivots to using tech to bring more ‘delight’ to health care
summary: Ratnakar Lavu spent most of his career working at major retailers. Here's why Lavu thinks his experience can bring 'delight' to the healthcare sector.

headline: Acadia Healthcare Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates on Rising Admissions
summary: ACHC tops Q4 estimates as admissions and patient days rise, lifting revenues, but profit plunges 89% year over year.
